Problem: VMs were using NAT Network (itlui) which required port forwarding to allow external SSH access.
Port Forwarding Rules Created:
NameHost PortGuest IPGuest PortSSH222210.0.2.1522SSH2222310.0.2.1422SSH3222410.0.2.1422
Windows Firewall Rules Added:
powershellNew-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName "VirtualBox SSH" -Direction Inbound -Protocol TCP -LocalPort 2222 -Action Allow -Profile Any
New-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName "VirtualBox SSH2" -Direction Inbound -Protocol TCP -LocalPort 2223 -Action Allow -Profile Any
